<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no" />
<title>冒险者公会：据点经营与远征</title>
<style>
:root{--bg:#0b1020;--panel:rgba(20,24,42,.96);--text:#eef2ff;--muted:#a8b0d5;--accent:#7c9cff;--good:#57d38c;--warn:#ffcb6b;--bad:#ff6b8b;--line:rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
*{box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
body{margin:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#090d1a 0%,#10162b 100%);color:var(--text);font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,"PingFang SC","Microsoft YaHei",sans-serif}
.app{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:12px}
.card{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;padding:14px;margin-bottom:12px;box-shadow:0 14px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.25)}
h1,h2{margin:0 0 10px}
p{color:var(--muted);line-height:1.55}
.row{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
button{border:0;border-radius:14px;padding:11px 13px;color:var(--text);background:var(--accent);font-weight:700}
button.secondary{background:#273154}
button.good{background:#2fa862}
button.warn{background:#d9a62f;color:#121212}
button.bad{background:#d94c6f}
.tabs{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:10px 0}
.stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:8px}
.stat{padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}
.stat .l{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}
.stat .v{font-size:18px;font-weight:800;margin-top:4px}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;gap:12px}
.list{display:grid;gap:10px}
.item{padding:12px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}
.head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px}
.name{font-weight:800;font-size:16px}
.tag{display:inline-block;margin-top:4px;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:999px;background:rgba(124,156,255,.16);font-size:12px}
.mini{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5}
.bar{height:9px;background:#222847;border-radius:999px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:5px}
.bar>span{display:block;height:100%;border-radius:999px}
.hp>span{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#5edb95,#2fb56c)}
.sta>span{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ffd66d,#d9a62f)}
.xp>span{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#c78bff,#7c9cff)}
.mana>span{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#71d8ff,#7c9cff)}
.smallgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:8px}
.chip{padding:7px 9px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}
.log{height:320px;overflow:auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;padding-right:3px}
.entry{padding:10px 12px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);font-size:13px;line-height:1.45}
.entry.good{border-color:rgba(87,211,140,.26)}
.entry.warn{border-color:rgba(255,203,107,.26)}
.entry.bad{border-color:rgba(255,107,139,.26)}
.two{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px}
.kv{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:4px}
.prog{height:8px;background:#232948;border-radius:999px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:6px}
.prog>span{display:block;height:100%;border-radius:999px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#7c9cff,#9d6cff)}
.footer{margin-top:10px;color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;line-height:1.5}
@media (max-width:960px){.grid,.two{grid-template-columns:1fr}.smallgrid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.log{height:220px}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="app">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>冒险者公会：据点经营与远征</h1>
    <p>招募冒险者、安排驻守、经营据点、派队远征、推进地图。粮食、木材、石料、金币、名望、士气和防御会彼此影响。</p>
    <div class="row">
      <button id="raid" class="warn">立即远征</button>
      <button id="save" class="secondary">保存</button>
      <button id="reset" class="bad">重开</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card stats" id="stats"></div>

  <div class="tabs">
    <button data-tab="hub" class="secondary">公会大厅</button>
    <button data-tab="heroes" class="secondary">冒险者</button>
    <button data-tab="tasks" class="secondary">委托任务</button>
    <button data-tab="base" class="secondary">据点经营</button>
    <button data-tab="map" class="secondary">世界地图</button>
    <button data-tab="log" class="secondary">事件记录</button>
  </div>

  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card" id="main"></div>
    <div>
      <div class="card">
        <h2>当前局势</h2>
        <div class="smallgrid" id="quick"></div>
        <div class="item" id="mapinfo" style="margin-top:10px"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h2>提示</h2>
        <p>据点经营是核心：农田、伐木场、采石场会产出资源，厨房和旅馆提升恢复，围墙提升防御，仓库决定你能囤多少。驻守成员会进一步提高产量。</p>
        <div class="footer">单文件网页版版本可直接在手机浏览器运行，下面的安卓工程会把它装进 WebView 里。后续还可以继续扩转职树、技能动画和更复杂的城市事件。</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
